## Determinism Validation

- All aging calculations use integer ages and fixed rates (no RNG).
- Post-processing uses tick-based seed (`tick.wrapping_mul(0x9e37_79b9)`) for reproducible grain.
- Health/energy penalties computed via SoA iteration (order-independent within tick).

Future WASM parity tests (Phase 2.4) will validate identical aging outcomes between native and wasm32 builds given same seed.

# Configuration Examples

## Gentle Aging (Long Lifespan)

```rust
ScriptBotsConfig {
    aging_health_decay_start: 20_000,      // ~16 minutes at 20 TPS
    aging_health_decay_rate: 0.001,        // 0.1% health/tick after threshold
    aging_health_decay_max: 0.05,          // Cap at 5% health/tick
    aging_energy_penalty_rate: 0.5,        // 50% of health penalty
    metabolism_ramp_floor: 1.0,
    metabolism_ramp_rate: 0.0,             // No boost ramping
    metabolism_boost_penalty: 0.0,
    ..default
}
```

Agents live ~16 minutes before decay, then gradually weaken. Boost remains viable throughout lifespan.

## Harsh Aging (Short Lifespan, Punishing Boost)

```rust
ScriptBotsConfig {
    aging_health_decay_start: 5_000,       // ~4 minutes
    aging_health_decay_rate: 0.005,        // 0.5% health/tick
    aging_health_decay_max: 0.1,           // Cap at 10% health/tick
    aging_energy_penalty_rate: 2.0,        // 200% of health penalty
    metabolism_ramp_floor: 1.5,            // Boost costs 1.5× base even at age 0
    metabolism_ramp_rate: 0.02,            // +2% per tick while boosting
    metabolism_boost_penalty: 0.08,        // Flat 8% health cost
    ..default
}
```

Agents die young (~4-5 minutes), and boost becomes lethal after age 100. Encourages conservative energy management and early reproduction.

## Tournament Mode (Disabled Aging)

```rust
ScriptBotsConfig {
    aging_health_decay_rate: 0.0,          // No decay
    aging_energy_penalty_rate: 0.0,
    metabolism_ramp_rate: 0.0,             // No boost penalty
    metabolism_boost_penalty: 0.0,
    ..default
}
```

Agents do not age; fitness determined purely by neural strategy.

